Class CompositeField

java.lang.Object

      gov.nih.nci.cabig.caaers.web.fields.CompositeField
All Implemented Interfaces:
InputField
public class CompositeField
extends AbstractInputField

An InputField which actually should be rendered as multiple HTML inputs. The multiple inputs are provided as an InputFieldGroup; the effective property names of the fields in that group will be (the property name of the CompositeField) + '.' + (the property name of the field in the group)

Author:
Rhett Sutphin, Ion C. Olaru
